00:21:20.760 --> 00:21:23.270
criticizing Joel;

00:21:23.280 --> 00:21:26.030
I just know there's a plateau

00:21:26.040 --> 00:21:30.350
in every ministry

00:21:30.360 --> 00:21:32.670
unless you keep grabbing and don't become

00:21:32.680 --> 00:21:34.830
comfortable and satisfied

00:21:34.840 --> 00:21:36.470
with where you are.

00:21:37.920 --> 00:21:41.230
Pastor Chip

00:21:41.240 --> 00:21:42.790
always talks about championship teams.

00:21:42.800 --> 00:21:43.790
Did

00:21:43.790 --> 00:21:43.800
the

00:21:43.800 --> 00:21:46.110
Kansas City Chiefs become

00:21:46.120 --> 00:21:47.470
comfortable

00:21:47.480 --> 00:21:50.310
after they won so many times?

00:21:50.320 --> 00:21:51.910
Why were they so

00:21:51.920 --> 00:21:53.750
terrible last year?

00:21:53.760 --> 00:21:54.870
They had the same

00:21:54.880 --> 00:21:58.190
players, but they were really bad

00:21:58.190 --> 00:21:58.200
and

00:21:58.200 --> 00:21:59.390
weren't fun to watch

00:21:59.390 --> 00:21:59.400
anymore.

00:21:59.400 --> 00:22:01.870
You

00:22:01.880 --> 00:22:03.950
become complacent.

00:22:06.600 --> 00:22:08.830
The Golden State

00:22:08.840 --> 00:22:10.430
Warriors were good for a

00:22:10.440 --> 00:22:12.190
while with Steph Curry and

00:22:12.200 --> 00:22:14.110
were fun to watch. You had

00:22:14.120 --> 00:22:16.550
a dynasty there that fell

00:22:16.560 --> 00:22:18.550
apart. The same thing happened with

00:22:18.560 --> 00:22:21.630
Michael Jordan's

00:22:21.630 --> 00:22:21.640
team.

00:22:21.640 --> 00:22:23.030
I don't ever want to be that

00:22:23.040 --> 00:22:26.190
championship team that falls apart

00:22:26.200 --> 00:22:28.070
for the Lord. You should always

00:22:28.070 --> 00:22:28.080
be

00:22:28.080 --> 00:22:30.030
grabbing, pulling yourself

00:22:30.040 --> 00:22:31.669
up, going from glory to

00:22:31.679 --> 00:22:32.710
glory,

00:22:32.720 --> 00:22:35.150
and not being satisfied with repeating

00:22:35.160 --> 00:22:38.830
somebody else's words.

00:22:38.840 --> 00:22:44.390
I

00:22:44.400 --> 00:22:46.110
want to challenge you to

00:22:46.120 --> 00:22:48.110
keep growing

00:22:48.110 --> 00:22:48.120
and

00:22:48.120 --> 00:22:49.669
seeking

00:22:49.679 --> 00:22:51.390
Him.

00:22:51.400 --> 00:22:53.790
There's always something new you

00:22:53.800 --> 00:22:56.550
can learn from the Holy Spirit.

00:22:56.560 --> 00:22:59.310
I like George Washington Carver,

00:22:59.320 --> 00:23:01.390
the man who talked with the flowers.

00:23:01.400 --> 00:23:03.830
Sister Billie introduced that book,

00:23:03.840 --> 00:23:05.270
and she always talks about George

00:23:05.280 --> 00:23:06.910
Washington Carver. He was

00:23:06.910 --> 00:23:06.920
an

00:23:06.920 --> 00:23:09.750
African-American man during

00:23:09.750 --> 00:23:09.760
a

00:23:09.760 --> 00:23:13.110
hard time with

00:23:13.120 --> 00:23:14.669
prejudice and racism,

00:23:14.679 --> 00:23:17.710
but he prevailed and

00:23:24.720 --> 00:23:28.030
was able to

00:23:28.040 --> 00:23:31.230
succeed whenever most African-Americans weren't.

00:23:31.240 --> 00:23:33.510
He had that

00:23:33.520 --> 00:23:35.990
bulldog

00:23:35.990 --> 00:23:36.000
mentality:

00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:37.550
"I'm going to make it.

00:23:37.560 --> 00:23:38.990
I don't care what

00:23:38.990 --> 00:23:39.000
anyone

00:23:39.000 --> 00:23:40.590
else says; I'm

00:23:40.600 --> 00:23:44.750
going to do what God's called me to do."I

00:23:44.750 --> 00:23:44.760
respect

00:23:44.760 --> 00:23:46.510
George Washington Carver.

00:23:46.520 --> 00:23:48.710
I read his

00:23:48.720 --> 00:23:50.550
book, "The Man Who Talked with the

00:23:50.550 --> 00:23:50.560
flowers."My

00:23:50.560 --> 00:23:52.590
God, that guy went

00:23:52.600 --> 00:23:56.870
through something

00:23:56.870 --> 00:23:56.880
in

00:23:56.880 --> 00:24:00.150
a

00:24:00.160 --> 00:24:02.510
very racist

00:24:02.520 --> 00:24:03.550
area,

00:24:03.560 --> 00:24:07.556
but

00:24:08.040 --> 00:24:11.110
he never let the racism define him.

00:24:11.120 --> 00:24:13.030
He became what God called him to

00:24:13.030 --> 00:24:13.040
be.

00:24:13.040 --> 00:24:14.390
He would get up every morning and

00:24:14.400 --> 00:24:17.390
talk to the Father, the Great Creator.

00:24:17.400 --> 00:24:19.110
He

00:24:19.120 --> 00:24:23.030
was a trailblazer.

00:24:23.040 --> 00:24:25.430
You can't let

00:24:25.440 --> 00:24:27.430
the color of your skin,

00:24:27.430 --> 00:24:27.440
your

00:24:27.440 --> 00:24:29.710
gender, or anything

00:24:29.710 --> 00:24:29.720
else

00:24:29.720 --> 00:24:31.750
tell you you're not good enough.

00:24:31.760 --> 00:24:34.710
When God puts His hand on you,

00:24:34.720 --> 00:24:38.590
I don't care what they say;

00:24:38.600 --> 00:24:41.270
you will be what God called you to be.

00:24:41.270 --> 00:24:41.280
When

00:24:41.280 --> 00:24:43.790
I was

00:24:45.720 --> 00:24:47.550
a janitor,

00:24:47.560 --> 00:24:49.870
I asked to preach the gospel,

00:24:49.870 --> 00:24:49.880
and

00:24:49.880 --> 00:24:51.830
they

00:24:51.830 --> 00:24:51.840
said,

00:24:51.840 --> 00:24:52.910
"No,

00:24:52.920 --> 00:24:54.717
you're a janitor; go clean.

00:24:55.760 --> 00:24:58.070
I don't see the call on your

00:24:58.070 --> 00:24:58.080
life."But

00:24:58.080 --> 00:25:00.230
I

00:25:00.230 --> 00:25:00.240
felt

00:25:00.240 --> 00:25:04.030
God told me.

00:25:11.320 --> 00:25:14.110
A lot of people may not see it,

00:25:14.120 --> 00:25:16.950
but Jesus does,

00:25:16.960 --> 00:25:19.150
and He said, "I want you to go on YouTube

00:25:19.160 --> 00:25:20.510
and

00:25:20.520 --> 00:25:22.190
pray."So,

00:25:22.200 --> 00:25:24.190
even if people don't acknowledge your

00:25:24.200 --> 00:25:26.870
call

00:25:26.880 --> 00:25:29.110
or

00:25:29.120 --> 00:25:30.830
want you

00:25:32.600 --> 00:25:34.390
in their inner circle, it doesn't matter. I

00:25:34.400 --> 00:25:36.830
always look for the camaraderie of things.

00:25:36.840 --> 00:25:38.550
How many times did

00:25:38.560 --> 00:25:40.990
Brother Kenneth Hagin hang out with Oral

00:25:41.000 --> 00:25:45.350
Roberts?

00:25:46.920 --> 00:25:49.310
I've

00:25:50.360 --> 00:25:53.430
never seen them preach together,

00:25:53.440 --> 00:25:55.390
but they were in the same city,

00:25:55.390 --> 00:25:55.400
almost

00:25:55.400 --> 00:25:57.230
on the same

00:25:57.240 --> 00:25:59.590
street.

00:26:06.560 --> 00:26:09.310
Yet, I hardly ever saw them

00:26:09.320 --> 00:26:11.750
preaching at each other's conferences.

00:26:11.760 --> 00:26:13.030
They had some of the biggest

00:26:13.040 --> 00:26:16.230
ministries. I drive by them and get inspired by the mega-church, the

00:26:16.230 --> 00:26:16.240
grounds, and the school. I drive by

00:26:16.240 --> 00:26:17.750
and look at the City of Faith,

00:26:17.760 --> 00:26:19.669
the big tower, and

00:26:19.669 --> 00:26:19.679
the things

00:26:19.679 --> 00:26:21.350
spinning on the top of the building.

00:26:27.960 --> 00:26:30.030
I drive

00:26:30.040 --> 00:26:31.550
around Oral Roberts University

00:26:31.550 --> 00:26:31.560
to

00:26:31.560 --> 00:26:33.470
keep

00:26:33.480 --> 00:26:36.790
myself inspired.

00:26:38.910 --> 00:26:38.920
Even

00:26:43.470 --> 00:26:43.480
if

00:26:45.960 --> 00:26:47.430
you

00:26:50.000 --> 00:26:51.630
have the same mission,

00:26:54.200 --> 00:26:55.990
some camps don't function with

00:26:55.990 --> 00:26:56.000
other

00:26:56.000 --> 00:26:57.950
camps. I'm

00:26:57.960 --> 00:26:59.150
learning

00:26:59.160 --> 00:27:00.750
because I'm in one of

00:27:00.760 --> 00:27:02.669
the greatest cities in the

00:27:02.679 --> 00:27:04.430
Bible Belt.

00:27:04.440 --> 00:27:06.110
And maybe I'm wrong. Maybe they hung out

00:27:06.120 --> 00:27:08.830
every day; I just never saw it on video because

00:27:08.830 --> 00:27:08.840
I watch

00:27:08.840 --> 00:27:10.870
all of them.

00:27:10.880 --> 00:27:12.550
But I hardly ever hear them

00:27:12.560 --> 00:27:14.390
talking about each other very often, even

00:27:14.400 --> 00:27:16.590
in their sermons. But yet they were that

00:27:16.600 --> 00:27:18.470
close together.

00:27:18.480 --> 00:27:19.390
You know what I'm saying? I mean, they're

00:27:19.400 --> 00:27:21.430
like less than five miles apart probably.

00:27:21.440 --> 00:27:22.790
And I'm thinking, because I drive over

00:27:22.800 --> 00:27:23.990
there, I'm looking and they're almost

00:27:24.000 --> 00:27:26.310
on the same street.

00:27:26.320 --> 00:27:28.150
But does that make them bad? No. It just

00:27:28.150 --> 00:27:28.160
means

00:27:28.160 --> 00:27:29.630
they did what they were

00:27:29.640 --> 00:27:31.590
called to do.

00:27:31.600 --> 00:27:32.990
And there's a whole lot of other

00:27:33.000 --> 00:27:34.510
ministries here.

00:27:34.520 --> 00:27:40.150
There's all kinds of churches in Tulsa.

00:27:40.160 --> 00:27:41.110
I don't know.

00:27:41.120 --> 00:27:42.950
I'm just learning,

00:27:42.960 --> 00:27:45.190
and I watch

00:27:45.200 --> 00:27:47.270
and I say, 'Hmm, this is all so interesting

00:27:47.280 --> 00:27:48.790
to

00:27:48.790 --> 00:27:48.800
me.'So

00:27:48.800 --> 00:27:50.710
people go, 'Well, boy, you

00:27:50.710 --> 00:27:50.720
treading

00:27:50.720 --> 00:27:52.310
on really

00:27:53.590 --> 00:27:53.600
soft,

00:27:55.240 --> 00:27:56.630
rice paper thin. You shouldn't say some

00:27:56.640 --> 00:27:58.310
of the things you say.'I ain't scared of

00:27:58.320 --> 00:27:59.310
it.

00:27:59.320 --> 00:28:00.910
I just look at it

00:28:00.920 --> 00:28:04.390
and I'm just real.

00:28:04.400 --> 00:28:06.630
I'm not trying to make

00:28:06.640 --> 00:28:07.830
something out of

00:28:07.840 --> 00:28:11.350
nothing, but I just watch.

00:28:13.360 --> 00:28:15.430
And like I said, maybe that's why I'm

00:28:15.440 --> 00:28:16.830
where I'm at and they are where

00:28:16.840 --> 00:28:19.710
they are at.

00:28:19.720 --> 00:28:21.470
I always ask the hard

00:28:21.480 --> 00:28:22.830
questions

00:28:22.840 --> 00:28:26.110
because I want to learn,

00:28:26.120 --> 00:28:27.710
because I want to go and be close to

00:28:27.720 --> 00:28:29.470
Him.

00:28:29.480 --> 00:28:31.790
Y'all have an opinion and it changes all

00:28:31.800 --> 00:28:32.909
the time.

00:28:32.919 --> 00:28:34.350
The same person who gets excited and

00:28:34.360 --> 00:28:36.870
tells me I'm good in one email is mad

00:28:36.880 --> 00:28:38.630
the next couple of days, telling me I'm

00:28:38.640 --> 00:28:40.669
going to hell.

00:28:40.679 --> 00:28:42.870
And I get them all the time. 'We really

00:28:42.880 --> 00:28:44.550
like you.'And then the next one, you're

00:28:44.560 --> 00:28:46.510
mad and you're saying profanity at me in

00:28:46.520 --> 00:28:48.830
emails. And I'm going,

00:28:50.600 --> 00:28:52.630
'That's interesting.'D goes, 'Isn't

00:28:52.640 --> 00:28:54.550
that interesting?'I said,

00:28:54.560 --> 00:29:01.350
'No, it's just

00:29:01.360 --> 00:29:02.270
people.'All

00:29:02.280 --> 00:29:03.350
right.

00:29:03.360 --> 00:29:04.669
So,

00:29:04.679 --> 00:29:07.390
be a trailblazer.

00:29:07.400 --> 00:29:09.070
Be somebody who is getting the rocks out

00:29:09.080 --> 00:29:10.870
of there like us.

00:29:10.880 --> 00:29:13.430
And when it's all said and done,

00:29:13.440 --> 00:29:15.190
no matter who's in your tent and

00:29:15.200 --> 00:29:17.790
who's in your camp, we're in a time like

00:29:17.800 --> 00:29:19.710
we've never seen before.

00:29:19.720 --> 00:29:21.070
And we're going to touch the nations for

00:29:21.080 --> 00:29:23.870
Jesus. And we may be the only ones in our

00:29:23.880 --> 00:29:25.510
little group—me, my

00:29:25.520 --> 00:29:27.230
son, and my wife—and we're all standing

00:29:27.240 --> 00:29:29.470
together. We don't have to have people

00:29:29.480 --> 00:29:30.830
in our corner

00:29:30.840 --> 00:29:33.149
being our cheerleader and telling us how

00:29:33.159 --> 00:29:35.710
great we are or what we're doing. Jesus

00:29:35.720 --> 00:29:37.950
already did that:

00:29:37.960 --> 00:29:40.990
'I love you, Brandon. Keep

00:29:41.000 --> 00:29:41.909
going.'And

00:29:41.919 --> 00:29:43.310
we just keep doing what He's asked

00:29:43.320 --> 00:29:46.270
us to do.

00:29:46.280 --> 00:29:48.030
And we're so excited that there are so

00:29:48.040 --> 00:29:49.670
many of you that show up and want to pray

00:29:49.680 --> 00:29:50.910
with us.

00:29:50.920 --> 00:29:52.590
But

00:29:52.600 --> 00:29:54.830
that's what I had to say tonight.

00:29:54.840 --> 00:29:56.310
Every single night, I always try to be a

00:29:56.320 --> 00:29:57.670
little different for things that are on

00:29:57.680 --> 00:29:59.790
my heart and things that I'm thinking.

00:29:59.800 --> 00:30:01.590
You say, 'That's Brandon's thoughts

00:30:03.225 --> 00:30:03.235
today.'All

00:30:06.360 --> 00:30:08.430
right. There. Now, tell them what you

00:30:08.440 --> 00:30:10.030
want to tell them because I told them what I

00:30:10.030 --> 00:30:10.040
felt

00:30:10.040 --> 00:30:14.270
like I wanted to say.

00:30:14.280 --> 00:30:17.670
You're done. What was it

00:30:17.670 --> 00:30:17.680
that happened?

00:30:17.680 --> 00:30:19.030
Yeah. I can go over some of the things

00:30:19.040 --> 00:30:20.630
we saw last night.

00:30:20.640 --> 00:30:22.070
We saw a lot.

00:30:22.080 --> 00:30:23.830
And I'm going to tell you this: after I

00:30:23.840 --> 00:30:25.950
saw what I saw, it shook me.

00:30:25.960 --> 00:30:28.150
And there's a lot of you that think that

00:30:28.160 --> 00:30:30.070
we're years

00:30:30.080 --> 00:30:32.070
and years away from Jesus Christ coming

00:30:32.080 --> 00:30:34.550
back, and you are greatly

00:30:34.560 --> 00:30:37.470
deceived. Jesus is coming, and He's

00:30:37.480 --> 00:30:39.110
coming very soon.

00:30:39.120 --> 00:30:41.950
And as I was looking into the Boston

00:30:41.960 --> 00:30:44.950
Marathon and things like that,

00:30:44.960 --> 00:30:47.590
praying over

00:30:48.240 --> 00:30:50.830
the 20th and the 18th—the Lord

00:30:50.840 --> 00:30:52.990
highlighted the 20th

00:30:52.990 --> 00:30:53.000
and

00:30:53.000 --> 00:30:54.550
the

00:30:54.550 --> 00:30:54.560
18th—and

00:30:54.560 --> 00:30:58.830
Coachella, praying over these oil

00:30:58.840 --> 00:31:01.670
wells. There was so much that the Lord

00:31:01.680 --> 00:31:03.990
had us praying for last night:

00:31:04.000 --> 00:31:05.950
praying over

00:31:05.960 --> 00:31:09.670
the NBA, praying over the NBA teams,

00:31:09.680 --> 00:31:12.510
certain ones. And like I said, I

00:31:12.520 --> 00:31:13.910
don't say a whole lot because there's a

00:31:13.920 --> 00:31:16.190
lot of you that gamble, and you go, 'Well,

00:31:16.200 --> 00:31:17.950
you're telling me to...'It's not a

00:31:17.960 --> 00:31:20.430
gamble. I pray over this and they

00:31:20.440 --> 00:31:22.590
start accusing me: 'Are you saying

00:31:22.600 --> 00:31:24.790
this team?

00:31:24.800 --> 00:31:26.510
Are you saying this team and this team

00:31:26.510 --> 00:31:26.520
are

00:31:26.520 --> 00:31:28.710
going to be together in the

00:31:28.710 --> 00:31:28.720
playoffs?'I'm

00:31:28.720 --> 00:31:30.590
telling you what I'm

00:31:30.600 --> 00:31:32.710
praying over. So then you want to go and

00:31:32.720 --> 00:31:34.470
gamble,

00:31:34.480 --> 00:31:36.950
and it's like, my God, what is wrong

00:31:36.960 --> 00:31:38.350
with the immaturity of some of these

00:31:38.360 --> 00:31:40.070
people? I'm not

00:31:40.080 --> 00:31:42.230
saying that. The Lord said to pray over these

00:31:42.240 --> 00:31:43.990
teams. You can pray over Boston. You can

00:31:44.000 --> 00:31:45.870
pray over New York. You can pray over

00:31:45.880 --> 00:31:48.350
these teams. Both look like they could

00:31:48.360 --> 00:31:51.270
be doing something in

00:31:51.280 --> 00:31:53.550
the future. I don't know. I don't follow

00:31:53.560 --> 00:31:56.150
sports a whole lot. The Lord just talks

00:31:56.160 --> 00:31:58.110
about sports because He knows I like

00:31:58.120 --> 00:31:59.990
the Thunder.

00:32:00.000 --> 00:32:02.270
And so,

00:32:02.280 --> 00:32:05.230
okay, this is very serious.

00:32:05.240 --> 00:32:08.830
Do you remember when I told you I saw a

00:32:08.840 --> 00:32:11.470
draft coming?

00:32:11.480 --> 00:32:12.910
Do you remember when I told you that

00:32:12.920 --> 00:32:15.390
they would use women in the draft?

00:32:15.400 --> 00:32:18.870
And I said I saw Trump being president

00:32:18.880 --> 00:32:21.669
during this time frame.

00:32:21.679 --> 00:32:25.950
I said, 'I saw a draft coming to America,

00:32:25.960 --> 00:32:27.430
and they didn't just

00:32:27.440 --> 00:32:30.510
draft the men; they drafted the

00:32:30.510 --> 00:32:30.520
women.'And

00:32:30.520 --> 00:32:33.630
I said, 'Pray against this.

00:32:33.640 --> 00:32:35.190
Pray against it.'Does anybody remember

00:32:35.200 --> 00:32:36.830
that? Put it in

00:32:36.830 --> 00:32:36.840
the comments

00:32:36.840 --> 00:32:38.669
section right now if you remember me

00:32:38.679 --> 00:32:41.110
talking about the draft and that they

00:32:41.120 --> 00:32:43.470
would draft your women too

00:32:43.480 --> 00:32:45.310
because they wanted to have equal

00:32:45.320 --> 00:32:46.550
rights. And I said women would be

00:32:46.560 --> 00:32:48.630
drafted too, and they would be called

00:32:48.640 --> 00:32:51.230
into service—a younger generation of

00:32:51.240 --> 00:32:53.669
women.

00:32:53.679 --> 00:32:56.070
Does anybody remember that? I saw it in

00:32:56.080 --> 00:32:57.190
the vision

00:32:57.200 --> 00:32:58.669
and we were praying over it, and I said

00:32:58.679 --> 00:32:59.750
they were going to Europe and they were

00:32:59.760 --> 00:33:02.030
going over places because we got struck

00:33:02.040 --> 00:33:05.669
on America's soil.

00:33:05.679 --> 00:33:07.150
I don't know if you all remember

00:33:07.160 --> 00:33:09.230
this; the Lord shows us quite a bit

00:33:09.240 --> 00:33:11.110
and we're grateful for everything. But

00:33:11.120 --> 00:33:13.790
now I want you to see what we prayed

00:33:13.800 --> 00:33:16.350
over a year and a half or two years ago is

00:33:16.360 --> 00:33:19.230
now in the news.

00:33:19.240 --> 00:33:29.350
Can you show them that

00:33:29.360 --> 00:33:33.270
now? That disturbed me a little bit.

00:33:33.280 --> 00:33:36.430
Is there more?

00:33:39.120 --> 00:33:45.910
So, you see

00:33:45.920 --> 00:33:48.030
they're talking about automatically

00:33:48.040 --> 00:33:51.030
doing all this and making sure your kids

00:33:51.040 --> 00:33:53.110
are ready for war. Now, I don't agree with that.

00:33:53.110 --> 00:33:53.120
I don't agree with any war,

00:33:53.120 --> 00:33:55.750
but especially forcing people to go

00:33:55.760 --> 00:33:57.669
fight if they didn't register for it

00:33:57.679 --> 00:34:00.030
and they don't want to do it.

00:34:00.040 --> 00:34:02.310
But it's sad

00:34:02.320 --> 00:34:05.669
because I told you I saw it coming,

00:34:05.679 --> 00:34:07.950
what the Lord showed us about a

00:34:07.960 --> 00:34:09.389
major draft

00:34:09.399 --> 00:34:10.750
and that they would have to do it in the

00:34:10.760 --> 00:34:13.149
days ahead. And so many women

00:34:13.159 --> 00:34:15.110
got so upset about it and freaked out

00:34:15.120 --> 00:34:16.990
about it. Now, I'm trying to tell you

00:34:17.000 --> 00:34:18.470
what the Lord showed me. And I'm not

00:34:18.480 --> 00:34:20.310
trying to stir up fear. I'm trying to

00:34:20.320 --> 00:34:22.270
tell you we must pray because

00:34:22.270 --> 00:34:22.280
of

00:34:22.280 --> 00:34:24.669
even what I told you last night.

00:34:24.679 --> 00:34:25.909
Okay, this is what I thought was

00:34:25.919 --> 00:34:27.270
interesting.

00:34:27.280 --> 00:34:29.230
Thank you, Holy Spirit.

00:34:29.240 --> 00:34:31.149
He starts helping me because I wait for

00:34:31.159 --> 00:34:32.630
the anointing to hit me, and then

00:34:32.640 --> 00:34:34.909
finally I start feeling it come on me.

00:34:34.919 --> 00:34:36.750
So, y'all have to bear with me because I

00:34:36.760 --> 00:34:38.830
can't do this without Him.

00:34:38.840 --> 00:34:41.349
But

00:34:41.359 --> 00:34:44.349
I saw a red cross.

00:34:44.359 --> 00:34:47.430
The Red Cross was over Boston and the

00:34:47.440 --> 00:34:49.510
Lord said, 'Pray over this time frame,

00:34:49.520 --> 00:34:52.149
for it will be about the Red

00:34:52.149 --> 00:34:52.159
Cross.'And

00:34:52.159 --> 00:34:53.550
I told you that. Does

00:34:53.550 --> 00:34:53.560
anyone

00:34:53.560 --> 00:34:55.190
remember that last night? And I said, 'I

00:34:55.200 --> 00:34:58.190
see a red cross. It's about hospitals.

00:34:58.200 --> 00:35:00.270
I see hospitals with red crosses on

00:35:00.270 --> 00:35:00.280
them.'See,

00:35:00.280 --> 00:35:02.349
I hear in part and I see in

00:35:02.359 --> 00:35:03.870
part, but a lot of times I don't know

00:35:03.880 --> 00:35:05.230
what I'm seeing.

00:35:05.240 --> 00:35:08.430
I just call out the vision of what I'm

00:35:08.440 --> 00:35:11.190
seeing as I'm praying. And I said, 'It's

00:35:11.200 --> 00:35:12.990
about a red cross.'And I said, 'There's a

00:35:13.000 --> 00:35:14.990
massive red cross, so much so that a

00:35:15.000 --> 00:35:17.790
helicopter could land on

00:35:17.790 --> 00:35:17.800
it.'Does

00:35:17.800 --> 00:35:19.470
anybody remember that? I said, 'I

00:35:19.480 --> 00:35:21.270
see it, and it looks like it's about

00:35:21.280 --> 00:35:22.790
hospitals.'So,

00:35:22.800 --> 00:35:24.950
not wanting to add to or take away

00:35:24.960 --> 00:35:28.550
from anything, the Red Cross has a

00:35:28.560 --> 00:35:31.670
Run for the Red Cross

00:35:31.680 --> 00:35:38.390
in Boston on the 18th.

00:35:38.400 --> 00:35:40.430
Pretty interesting, huh?

00:35:40.440 --> 00:35:42.710
It's a Red Cross. And I said, 'I see red

00:35:42.720 --> 00:35:45.030
crosses everywhere. It looks like

00:35:45.040 --> 00:35:49.430
hospitals.'Just

00:35:49.440 --> 00:35:51.070
remember that,

00:35:51.070 --> 00:35:51.080
because

00:35:51.080 --> 00:35:52.430
I don't know what I'm

00:35:52.430 --> 00:35:52.440
saying.

00:35:52.440 --> 00:35:54.950
But they take notes.

00:35:54.950 --> 00:35:54.960
Braden—he's

00:35:54.960 --> 00:35:56.590
over there taking notes. He has

00:35:56.600 --> 00:35:58.190
everything down and he's taking

00:35:58.200 --> 00:35:59.750
notes for everything the Lord's showing

00:35:59.750 --> 00:35:59.760
because

00:35:59.760 --> 00:36:03.470
he knows how the gift flows and he

00:36:03.480 --> 00:36:05.630
knows what we're looking

00:36:05.640 --> 00:36:09.670
for afterwards, because I can't stop and say,

00:36:09.680 --> 00:36:12.070
'Write this down.'Braden's trained and he

00:36:12.080 --> 00:36:16.349
knows exactly what we are

00:36:16.359 --> 00:36:20.390
looking for. Okay. So, the Red Cross

00:36:20.400 --> 00:36:23.110
runner, the Red Cross... see that? It's on

00:36:23.120 --> 00:36:26.110
April the 20th, right? So, it's during

00:36:26.120 --> 00:36:28.590
this time frame, but the Boston Marathon

00:36:28.600 --> 00:36:31.390
starts all next week and it goes for

00:36:31.400 --> 00:36:32.950
several days with several different

00:36:32.950 --> 00:36:32.960
kinds

00:36:32.960 --> 00:36:35.870
of events, from what I understand. But

00:36:35.880 --> 00:36:39.510
it's a red cross.

00:36:39.520 --> 00:36:41.030
So, isn't that kind of interesting how

00:36:41.040 --> 00:36:42.780
the Lord does that?

00:36:42.920 --> 00:36:45.030
I think it's interesting

00:36:45.030 --> 00:36:45.040
because

00:36:45.040 --> 00:36:46.630
I thought, 'Why am I seeing all these

00:36:46.630 --> 00:36:46.640
hospitals?'The

00:36:46.640 --> 00:36:48.870
Lord said, 'It's not about

00:36:48.870 --> 00:36:48.880
that.

00:36:48.880 --> 00:36:51.070
It's about the Red Cross. It's about

00:36:51.080 --> 00:36:52.790
this hospital.'And I thought, 'What are

00:36:52.800 --> 00:36:54.510
you showing

00:36:54.520 --> 00:36:55.950
me?'I

00:36:55.960 --> 00:36:58.070
said, 'The hospitals are in

00:36:58.080 --> 00:37:02.870
trouble,'because

00:37:02.880 --> 00:37:04.150
that's what I'm seeing. Hospitals

00:37:04.160 --> 00:37:05.830
are in trouble. What is it about this

00:37:05.840 --> 00:37:07.230
Red Cross?

00:37:07.240 --> 00:37:11.430
So then I saw a massive storm

00:37:11.440 --> 00:37:13.830
over Boston

00:37:13.840 --> 00:37:16.310
and I said it's over the New York area,

00:37:16.320 --> 00:37:18.230
all up there in the East. But I said this

00:37:18.240 --> 00:37:23.110
storm is so black, like onyx,

00:37:23.120 --> 00:37:26.390
that you can't see through it.

00:37:26.400 --> 00:37:28.430
And there are so many lightning bolts

00:37:28.440 --> 00:37:31.030
coming out of it. It looks like an electric

00:37:31.040 --> 00:37:32.310
storm.

00:37:32.320 --> 00:37:35.790
In this storm, it is so

00:37:35.800 --> 00:37:41.910
massive and so dark that it's coming,

00:37:41.920 --> 00:37:44.470
and I could see it. Then I saw

00:37:44.480 --> 00:37:47.349
people with shamrocks

00:37:47.359 --> 00:37:50.630
and green and white outfits and jerseys

00:37:50.640 --> 00:37:52.910
walking down the street.

00:37:52.920 --> 00:37:54.310
I said, 'I see these people

00:37:54.320 --> 00:37:56.430
celebrating

00:37:56.430 --> 00:37:56.440
basketball.'I

00:37:56.440 --> 00:38:01.110
said, 'Then I see the Knicks,

00:38:01.120 --> 00:38:03.270
the New York Knicks.'And I said, 'Watch

00:38:03.280 --> 00:38:05.390
these two

00:38:05.390 --> 00:38:05.400
teams.'What

00:38:05.400 --> 00:38:07.950
does that mean? I don't know.

00:38:07.960 --> 00:38:10.150
They're going to play each other.

00:38:10.160 --> 00:38:12.110
People said, 'Brandon,

00:38:12.120 --> 00:38:14.390
excuse me.'People said, 'Brandon,

00:38:14.400 --> 00:38:15.910
they're playing tonight,'which

00:38:15.910 --> 00:38:15.920
was

00:38:15.920 --> 00:38:17.910
tonight. Well, nothing happened. The

00:38:17.920 --> 00:38:20.230
game's over, thank God.

00:38:20.240 --> 00:38:22.030
They played tonight. That was

00:38:22.040 --> 00:38:23.910
the night before—the day

00:38:23.910 --> 00:38:23.920
before—and

00:38:23.920 --> 00:38:26.270
I said these two teams, I see them

00:38:26.280 --> 00:38:28.670
not knowing they were playing tonight.

00:38:34.440 --> 00:38:36.710
And the Lord said, 'You're not

00:38:36.720 --> 00:38:38.349
praying for

00:38:38.359 --> 00:38:39.590
tomorrow,'because

00:38:39.600 --> 00:38:42.230
I started interceding for the game

00:38:42.240 --> 00:38:43.910
and I told everybody it's not about

00:38:43.920 --> 00:38:45.790
today, it's not about the next couple

00:38:45.800 --> 00:38:47.630
of hours, not tomorrow. The Lord said,

00:38:47.640 --> 00:38:49.430
'This is something else.

00:38:49.440 --> 00:38:51.710
Keep praying over this.'Does anybody

00:38:51.720 --> 00:38:54.590
remember that? I said this is not about

00:38:54.600 --> 00:38:57.670
now. This is about something else. We

00:38:57.680 --> 00:39:00.030
must continue to pray over Boston and

00:39:00.040 --> 00:39:03.349
the Knicks.

00:39:03.359 --> 00:39:05.310
So, I was looking at all the different

00:39:05.320 --> 00:39:07.430
scenarios about Boston and the Knicks

00:39:07.440 --> 00:39:08.870
trying to figure out what the Lord is

00:39:08.880 --> 00:39:10.630
saying. You don't want to add to or

00:39:10.640 --> 00:39:12.870
take away from anything. Could they

00:39:12.880 --> 00:39:14.230
meet each other in the playoffs? Could

00:39:14.240 --> 00:39:15.590
they do this? Could they do that?

00:39:15.600 --> 00:39:16.910
You're trying to add it together. What

00:39:16.920 --> 00:39:19.830
is God saying? Then you get in trouble.

00:39:19.840 --> 00:39:21.830
He didn't say to do that. He didn't say

00:39:21.840 --> 00:39:23.070
that it was about the playoffs. He

00:39:23.080 --> 00:39:25.230
didn't say anything. He said, 'Pray over

00:39:25.240 --> 00:39:27.230
Boston and the

00:39:27.230 --> 00:39:27.240
Knicks.'And

00:39:27.240 --> 00:39:29.110
we cannot add to or take away from

00:39:29.120 --> 00:39:30.230
anything

00:39:30.230 --> 00:39:30.240
because

00:39:30.240 --> 00:39:32.270
if you do, you make a fool out of

00:39:32.280 --> 00:39:34.830
yourself and you

00:39:34.840 --> 00:39:36.590
don't know. And I said, 'You'll

00:39:36.600 --> 00:39:39.230
get more and more as you pray into this.

00:39:39.240 --> 00:39:41.430
God will show you more and more as you

00:39:41.440 --> 00:39:43.350
yield to Him,

00:39:43.360 --> 00:39:45.350
and He's going to show you more

00:39:45.360 --> 00:39:46.950
and more about the end times as you

00:39:46.960 --> 00:39:48.870
yield to Him.'And as I was sitting

00:39:48.880 --> 00:39:51.870
there, it all flashed before me.

00:39:51.880 --> 00:39:53.870
That's why I was trying to tell you how

00:39:53.880 --> 00:39:57.950
dark the tribulation truly is.

00:39:57.960 --> 00:40:01.790
I said, 'Y'all, from the

00:40:01.800 --> 00:40:04.150
leaders in Europe to all that's

00:40:04.150 --> 00:40:04.160
coming,'I

00:40:04.160 --> 00:40:05.950
said, 'My goodness,'as I was looking

00:40:05.960 --> 00:40:10.830
at it, it was coming at me so fast:

00:40:10.840 --> 00:40:14.550
the beast system, AI—and I could see AI

00:40:14.560 --> 00:40:17.510
and I could see a demon behind AI. But

00:40:17.520 --> 00:40:20.070
this demon was all part of the mark of

00:40:20.080 --> 00:40:22.630
the beast and the beast system

00:40:22.640 --> 00:40:25.790
and it was all coming out of AI.

00:40:25.800 --> 00:40:27.390
There was so much darkness in this,

00:40:27.400 --> 00:40:30.470
and we went over it all

00:40:30.480 --> 00:40:32.110
with

00:40:32.120 --> 00:40:33.590
a fine-tooth comb

00:40:33.600 --> 00:40:35.550
last night trying to go over things.

00:40:35.550 --> 00:40:35.560
Brandon

00:40:35.560 --> 00:40:37.750
kept

00:40:37.760 --> 00:40:39.270
bringing the notes out and we were going

00:40:39.280 --> 00:40:40.548
over things.

00:40:43.320 --> 00:40:45.550
I just know we're in the last days,

00:40:45.560 --> 00:40:47.270
and as I was praying into the revival

00:40:47.280 --> 00:40:49.750
and praying into the

00:40:49.760 --> 00:40:51.830
churches

00:40:51.840 --> 00:40:53.990
and what's coming to pray for the

00:40:54.000 --> 00:40:56.310
churches to wake up. The

00:40:56.320 --> 00:40:58.230
beginning of what I was just saying was

00:40:58.230 --> 00:40:58.240
that

00:40:58.240 --> 00:41:00.350
books like this are to stir

00:41:00.360 --> 00:41:03.270
yourself up to get ready so you can

00:41:03.280 --> 00:41:04.670
help

00:41:04.680 --> 00:41:07.270
plow the fields for

00:41:07.280 --> 00:41:08.910
what's about to take place. So, we're

00:41:08.920 --> 00:41:10.990
going to continue to pray. Then the

00:41:11.000 --> 00:41:13.790
other part was I saw boats

00:41:13.800 --> 00:41:15.510
with what

00:41:15.510 --> 00:41:15.520
looked

00:41:15.520 --> 00:41:20.790
like PVC pipes that were

00:41:20.800 --> 00:41:24.350
shooting off rockets—some kind

00:41:24.360 --> 00:41:28.870
of an explosive device in a long

00:41:28.870 --> 00:41:28.880
tube

00:41:28.880 --> 00:41:32.230
that was really strong.

00:41:34.960 --> 00:41:38.790
It was a homemade, homegrown

00:41:38.800 --> 00:41:40.950
rocket launcher

00:41:40.960 --> 00:41:42.710
that looked like something you'd set in

00:41:42.720 --> 00:41:44.150
a boat,

00:41:44.150 --> 00:41:44.160
with

00:41:44.160 --> 00:41:48.430
some C4 or whatever

00:41:48.440 --> 00:41:52.430
inside of it. And they lit it

00:41:52.440 --> 00:41:54.710
with a

00:41:54.720 --> 00:41:55.910
lighter.

00:41:55.910 --> 00:41:55.920
Boom!

00:41:55.920 --> 00:41:58.070
And this thing shot like a

00:41:58.080 --> 00:41:59.910
cannon.

00:41:59.920 --> 00:42:01.270
It shot up in the air and it was

00:42:01.280 --> 00:42:04.070
shooting into crowds

00:42:04.080 --> 00:42:06.590
from the river

00:42:09.720 --> 00:42:14.910
into power plants. I saw these men

00:42:14.920 --> 00:42:18.910
on these boats that were hiding the boat

00:42:18.920 --> 00:42:22.590
in the woods off of the river

00:42:22.600 --> 00:42:25.270
so that it would not be noticed. It

00:42:25.280 --> 00:42:27.470
was camouflaged

00:42:27.480 --> 00:42:30.190
with brush and stuff on top of it

00:42:30.200 --> 00:42:31.870
so that people would not know. And it was

00:42:31.880 --> 00:42:37.750
tied to a tree with a yellow rope.

00:42:37.760 --> 00:42:40.230
I could see these men

00:42:40.240 --> 00:42:42.870
and they were using fishing poles and

00:42:42.880 --> 00:42:46.630
they were fishing off of this boat going

00:42:46.640 --> 00:42:50.150
down the river or the streams.

00:42:50.160 --> 00:42:54.030
As one was fishing, the other was

00:42:54.040 --> 00:42:56.030
trolling with the

00:42:56.040 --> 00:42:58.310
motor on the boat and the other was

00:42:58.320 --> 00:43:01.950
taking pictures subtly

00:43:01.960 --> 00:43:04.350
doing surveillance and recon. The Lord

00:43:04.360 --> 00:43:06.790
called it recon last night.

00:43:06.800 --> 00:43:09.990
He said, 'They're doing recon.'So I saw

00:43:10.000 --> 00:43:14.750
them taking pictures of power plants,

00:43:14.760 --> 00:43:18.110
tourist destinations where people are

00:43:18.120 --> 00:43:20.670
not alert and just kind of having a good

00:43:20.680 --> 00:43:22.110
time.

00:43:22.120 --> 00:43:24.510
And they were on a boat like in New

00:43:24.520 --> 00:43:25.950
Orleans

00:43:25.960 --> 00:43:28.350
in these areas where they were just kind

00:43:28.360 --> 00:43:30.630
of messing around acting like they

00:43:30.640 --> 00:43:32.550
were fishing. I don't know, like in

00:43:32.560 --> 00:43:34.870
a city. I don't

00:43:34.880 --> 00:43:36.150
want to call out New Orleans because I don't

00:43:36.160 --> 00:43:37.910
know what city it was, but it looked

00:43:37.920 --> 00:43:39.270
like something like that—like

00:43:39.270 --> 00:43:39.280
the Mississippi—a

00:43:39.280 --> 00:43:41.430
boat where they were

00:43:41.440 --> 00:43:43.150
out there trolling around and they

00:43:43.160 --> 00:43:45.070
were fishing. Oh, and he had a fishing

00:43:45.080 --> 00:43:47.390
hat on with a fishing vest and a

00:43:47.400 --> 00:43:50.910
life vest, and they looked the part.

00:43:50.920 --> 00:43:52.670
But the Lord said they're doing this

00:43:52.680 --> 00:43:55.470
because they would bring

00:43:57.560 --> 00:44:00.030
suspicion.

00:44:02.240 --> 00:44:05.349
They were sus. And I don't know why

00:44:05.359 --> 00:44:08.670
that word's so hard for me.

00:44:09.680 --> 00:44:10.910
It's been that way

00:44:10.910 --> 00:44:10.920
a

00:44:10.920 --> 00:44:13.910
long, long time. They were all so

00:44:13.920 --> 00:44:15.070
sus.

00:44:15.080 --> 00:44:17.355
And Brandon, I love you.

00:44:18.080 --> 00:44:22.070
They're just so sus.

00:44:25.080 --> 00:44:26.750
They didn't want to draw attention to

00:44:26.760 --> 00:44:28.470
themselves if they were in a city taking

00:44:28.480 --> 00:44:30.670
pictures and acting like a bunch of dudes

00:44:30.680 --> 00:44:31.790
walking around that look like

00:44:31.790 --> 00:44:31.800
terrorists,

00:44:31.800 --> 00:44:34.830
because

00:44:34.840 --> 00:44:36.470
people are going to start noticing

00:44:36.480 --> 00:44:38.510
you doing that. So these dudes are out

00:44:38.520 --> 00:44:40.910
there floating around in a boat fishing

00:44:40.920 --> 00:44:43.030
and that was their recon mission.

00:44:43.040 --> 00:44:46.150
I saw the plans on the wall

00:44:46.160 --> 00:44:49.670
in their

00:44:49.680 --> 00:44:51.870
apartment complexes. They had

00:44:51.880 --> 00:44:54.670
blueprints of things that they had done

00:44:54.680 --> 00:44:58.670
with drones to do this recon over

00:44:58.670 --> 00:44:58.680
time—of

00:44:58.680 --> 00:45:02.190
power

00:45:02.200 --> 00:45:05.230
plants, gas structures where they're

00:45:05.240 --> 00:45:08.030
